{"tid":703043,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"巴打小心 網上申請網上行被騙","createTime":"2018-06-15T11:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T10:39:40.000Z","uid":16771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"921ad474981fe0a5bbe8509621c187c91a341b17","tid":703043,"uid":16771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T11:55:46.000Z","msg":"是咁的 本身用開hkbn <br />\n3月嘅時侯諗住轉網上行 咁就上網搵下sales 問下價<br />\n跟住搵到呢個sales<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/193556_4a47a0db6e60853dedfcfdf08a5ca249.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F193556_4a47a0db6e60853dedfcfdf08a5ca249.png&h=4d3af0f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/193649_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F193649_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=074f78b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/193656_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F193656_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=19931a32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁見佢有世界盃通行證幾吸引就決定申請 交埋用緊hkbn既證明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/193656_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F193656_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg&h=b1d54f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n交晒資料咁就錄埋音<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/193657_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F193657_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg&h=46545a40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n裝左now tv之後都無乜用過 諗住都係等世界盃先開黎睇<br />\n但琴晚發覺睇唔到<br />\n今日打上去pccw問 佢話3月份佢地無做 hkbn客戶轉台送世界盃通行證呢個優惠<br />\n話sales會唔會係指now tv 入面viutv播世界盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\npccw叫我搵返個sales 但宜家已經搵唔到個sales<br />\ntg last seen11/6 whatsapp last seen 琴日2040 打電話無人聽<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/195328_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F195328_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg&h=22689333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/195328_fe5df232cafa4c4e0f1a0294418e5660.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F195328_fe5df232cafa4c4e0f1a0294418e5660.jpg&h=4a8b2d3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請問我除左去消委會投訴仲有咩可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪得我咁on9中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46fe8cb7c20c2d3d8927646285e2f4bcd580665","tid":703043,"uid":35667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:01:56.000Z","msg":"send email去客服先會理"},{"pid":"cbe4c31bd2615be931bb43d9c8fb85ea140feff2","tid":703043,"uid":16771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f46fe8cb7c20c2d3d8927646285e2f4bcd580665","tid":703043,"uid":35667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:01:56.000Z","msg":"send email去客服先會理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:16:09.000Z","msg":"thx巴打 會試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb8c3dfd7bf7e176accda7731463065eb3b0456","tid":703043,"uid":152029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:55:58.000Z","msg":"有機會係resign 左既同事 巴打請tg 我 我係online 部門同事 我會幫返你處理有關投訴<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/FH2328\" da